  "description": "This individual presents as a reanimated human corpse, the skinTone set to zombie and stretched tight over prominent cheekbones and a narrow jaw. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets, fixed in an unblinking stare that conveys the absent discipline typical of the Hollow’s dead. White hair persists in sparse, uneven lengths, with a receded hairline that exposes a ridged brow and scalp scarring from old trauma. The body is lean and desiccated, with bony hands and elongated fingers that emphasize a predatory, grasping silhouette.",
